  tutorialTexts:
  - Welcome to\n <size=200%>Click and Buy</size>
  - The stock market has been so unpredictable and the experts don't know what to
    do...
  - So they sent YOU!\nYes, someone without an ioda of an idea how to navigate the
    market.\n\nSince nobody knew what's going on, taking a shot on a random guy coudln't
    hurt.
  - Little did they know the holy Stock Market Gods were on your side, making you
    able to alter the market given enough offeings ($money$).
  - Are you ready to show them you're not just an average trader Joe?\nGet filthy
    reach and prove them they shouldn't go around giving chances to money hungry
    lunatics with power of God and the Stock Market on their side!
  fadeInTextFeedback: {fileID: 0}
  currentTextIndex: 0
